{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66",
    "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
    "bookSlug": "psalms",
    "chapterNumber": 66,
    "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66",
    "summary": "Source text for Psalms 66 in Church Slavonic (Elizabeth Bible)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.1",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:1",
      "text": "В конец, в песнех, псалом песни Давиду.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.2",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:2",
      "text": "Боже, ущедри ны и благослови ны, просвети лице Твое на ны и помилуй ны:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.3",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:3",
      "text": "познати на земли путь Твой, во всех языцех спасение Твое.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.4",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:4",
      "text": "Да исповедятся Тебе людие, Боже, да исповедятся Тебе людие вси.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.5",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:5",
      "text": "Да возвеселятся и да возрадуются языцы: яко судиши людем правотою, и языки на земли наставиши.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.6",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:6",
      "text": "Да исповедятся Тебе людие, Боже, да исповедятся Тебе людие вси.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.7",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:7",
      "text": "Земля даде плод свой: благослови ны, Боже, Боже наш,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:psalms.66.8",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 66,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 66:8",
      "text": "благослови ны, Боже: и да убоятся Его вси концы земли.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
